{"id":248,"idInBook":427,"chapterId":2,"bookId":17,"arabic":"وَأَصْلُهُ فِي اَلْبُخَارِيِّ .‏  1‏‏1 ‏- انظر ( 8 / 65 / فتح )‏ ووقع في رواية الإسماعيلي مثل ما وقع في \" سنن البيهقي \" كما قال الحافظ في \" الفتح \" .‏","english":{"narrator":"","text":"And its basic meaning is found in Sahih al-Bukhari."},"hadithNumber":427,"hadithId":248,"reference":"2:248","meta":{"id":"bulugh_almaram","length":1767,"totalChapters":16,"arabic":{"title":"بلوغ المرام","author":"الإمام ابن حجر العسقلاني"},"english":{"title":"Bulugh Al Maram","author":"Ibn Hajar al-Asqalani"}},"chapter":{"id":2,"bookId":17,"arabic":"كتاب الصلاة","english":"The Book of Prayer","startHadith":180,"endHadith":640,"totalHadiths":461},"version":{"name":"bulugh_almaram","title":"Bulugh Al Maram","chapters":16}}